data.description: Make this 4-5 bedroom home your own! The large yard, spacious deck, wrap around porch, and a detached pole barn garage make this a perfect home to relax and enjoy guests. The main floor is comprised of a formal dining room, living room, laundry, and kitchen with newer cabinets and backsplash. There's also a large main floor area that could be finished as a main floor primary bedroom suite or open concept living, kitchen, & dining room. The second story has a primary bedroom suite, 3 additional bedrooms and a full hallway bath. The partial unfinished basement is ideal for storage. The 30 x 40 pole barn is equipped with cement, electricity, and the floor is plumbed and ready for a boiler system. With a few finishing touches you can have the home of your dreams! This home is being sold as is.
